        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 81. Pelidnota viridana Blanchard (female specimen compared with Blanchard's syntype by Ohaus which is deposited at MNHN) (valid name Pelidnota rostrata Burmeister). A Dorsal habitus B Lateral habitus C Specimen labels." , "Figure 80. Pelidnota rostrata Burmeister (male specimen compared with Burmeister's syntype by Ohaus from the Weber Collection). A Dorsal habitus B Lateral habitus C Specimen labels and male genitalia D Male genitalia, lateral view E Male parameres, dorsal view." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/130509" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/130508" .

